    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色及相關資訊",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "推薦角色",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 23,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Venti_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "溫迪",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "溫迪的大招可以造成多次傷害，迅速疊滿4層【追思之符】，為後續上場的隊友提供增益。該武器的副屬性（元素充能效率）可以極高提升溫迪大招的釋放頻率，最大化聚怪的功能。與此同時，在合適的配合下，溫迪的大招可以快速觸發多次元素反應，而這把武器提供的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "加成能夠有效提升這些元素反應造成的傷害。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2252,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Yelan_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "夜蘭",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器可以極大地提高夜蘭的元素充能效率，同時，夜蘭在使用元素戰技和元素爆發時可以迅速觸發該武器的特效，提升隊伍中所有角色的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "和攻擊力，比較適合夜蘭使用。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 28,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Ganyu_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "甘雨",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "若甘雨的定位是隊伍中的輔助型角色，該武器元素爆發能造成大量傷害，從而迅速疊滿武器特效來提高主C的傷害，同時副詞條的元素充能效率也很適合輔助型的甘雨。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2268,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/08/24/7998136/37a18b6b6865c59063003a9380f08225_1266672008615328646.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "柯萊",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器可以提高柯萊的元素充能效率，在他穩定觸發技能的同時，可以為全隊增加攻擊力與",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素精通",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Kujou Sara_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "九條裟羅",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "到達四命以後，九條裟羅的大招可以快速造成多次傷害，迅速疊滿4枚【追思之符】，為後續上場的隊友提供增益。同時，武器的副屬性（元素充能效率）能夠有效降低九條裟羅的高能耗大招元素能量球的需求量。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Gorou_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "五郎",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "五郎作為一名依靠元素戰技和元素爆發輔助隊友的角色，該武器的副詞條能夠解決五郎元素爆發的充能問題，並且後臺觸發武器特效可以提高隊友的輸出能力，精通增加的結晶盾厚度也可以提高生存率，是比較適合輔助型五郎的一把武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
